title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 6 2022
description:
Investigative journalist, Alex Berenson, joins C&B for a phenomenal conversation about his Twitter reinstatement, a covid update, including some new findings that will alarm everyone. Dutch farmers standing up and refusing to accept the insane policies of the environmental wackos in government. They are protesting by pouring manure on government buildings and blocking highways with tractors. Elon Musk has some questions about Twitter's banning of Alex Berenson.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
